data.description: Buyers will enjoy this beautiful, quiet community located in prime school district. This single story home offers 2659 sq. ft. of living space with 4 bedrooms, 2 baths and a 2 car garage. You'll find 9 ft. ceilings and tile flooring throughout the home which features formal living and dining area. The kitchen features granite counter tops, including a breakfast bar overlooking family room, white cabinetry, gas range and a large walk-in pantry. The master bedroom includes a walk-in closet and separate ensuite bath with garden tub, glass shower and double vanity sinks. The 3 additional bedrooms have ample storage space with walk-in closets. Enjoy quiet evenings on an extended covered patio that offers a peaceful conservation view. "No CDD fees, learn how that impacts your buying power."
